diatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fmore-sports%2Fothers%2Ftoisa-2024-a-tribute-to-sporting-excellence-dedication-and-glory%2Farticleshow%2F118471578.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What%20Microsoft's%20Majorana%201%20Means%20For%20Quantum%20Computing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20introduced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmicrosoft-unveils-revolutionary-quantum-chip-satya-nadella-explains-how-it-works-7754059%5C%22%3EMajorana%201%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20groundbreaking%20quantum%20chip%20designed%20to%20bring%20industrial-scale%20quantum%20computing%20within%20reach%20in%20just%20a%20few%20years.%20Built%20on%20a%20revolutionary%20Topological%20Core%20architecture%2C%20this%20chip%20harnesses%20topoconductors%20-%20a%20material%20capable%20of%20stabilising%20and%20controlling%20Majorana%20particles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20makes%20qubits%20more%20reliable%20and%20scalable%2C%20bringing%20quantum%20computing%20closer%20to%20real-world%20use.%20Experts%20say%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20big%20advances%20in%20healthcare%2C%20climate%20science%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20quantum%20computing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuantum%20computing%20is%20a%20new%20way%20of%20processing%20information%20using%20the%20principles%20of%20quantum%20mechanics.%20Unlike%20regular%20computers%20that%20use%20bits%20(0s%20and%201s)%2C%20quantum%20computers%20use%20qubits%2C%20which%20can%20be%20both%200%20and%201%20at%20the%20same%20time%20due%20to%20superposition.%20They%20also%20use%20entanglement%2C%20where%20qubits%20are%20linked%20and%20affect%20each%20other%20instantly%2C%20making%20calculations%20much%20faster.%20This%20allows%20quantum%20computers%20to%20solve%20complex%20problems%20in%20minutes%20that%20would%20take%20traditional%20computers%20years.%20They%20have%20potential%20in%20areas%20like%20cybersecurity%2C%20drug%20discovery%2C%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Majorana%201%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajorana%201%20is%20the%20world's%20first%20quantum%20chip%20using%20Topological%20Core%20architecture.%20It%20introduces%20topoconductors%2C%20a%20new%20class%20of%20materials%20that%20can%20observe%20and%20control%20Majorana%20particles%20-%20exotic%20quantum%20particles%20that%20allow%20for%20stable%20and%20error-resistant%20quantum%20operations.%20Microsoft%20compares%20this%20advancement%20to%20the%20invention%20of%20semiconductors%2C%20which%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20modern%20electronics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20approach%20aims%20to%20build%20quantum%20computers%20with%20a%20million%20qubits%20-%20a%20threshold%20necessary%20for%20solving%20real-world%20industrial%20and%20scientific%20challenges.%20Current%20supercomputers%2C%20even%20if%20combined%2C%20cannot%20perform%20the%20calculations%20that%20a%20one-million-qubit%20quantum%20computer%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20took%20a%20step%20back%20and%20said%20'OK%2C%20let's%20invent%20the%20transistor%20for%20the%20quantum%20age.%20What%20properties%20does%20it%20need%20to%20have%3F'%26quot%3B%20said%20Chetan%20Nayak%2C%20Microsoft%20technical%20fellow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20really%20how%20we%20got%20here%20-%20it's%20the%20particular%20combination%2C%20the%20quality%20and%20the%20important%20details%20in%20our%20new%20materials%20stack%20that%20have%20enabled%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20qubit%20and%20ultimately%20our%20entire%20architecture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20experts%20say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20latest%20quantum%20computing%20breakthrough%20has%20generated%20excitement%2C%20experts%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcj3e3252gj8o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20more%20data%20is%20needed%20to%20fully%20assess%20its%20impact.%20The%20significance%20of%20the%20research%20-%20and%20its%20potential%20effect%20on%20quantum%20computing%20-%20remains%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJensen%20Huang%2C%20CEO%20of%20Nvidia%2C%20said%20in%20January%20that%20%26quot%3Buseful%26quot%3B%20quantum%20computing%20was%20still%2020%20years%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nayak%20suggests%20the%20new%20advancements%20could%20challenge%20traditional%20timelines.%20%26quot%3BMany%20people%20have%20said%20that%20quantum%20computing%2C%20that%20is%20to%20say%20useful%20quantum%20computers%2C%20are%20decades%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20this%20brings%20us%20into%20years%20rather%20than%20decades.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETravis%20Humble%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Quantum%20Science%20Centre%20at%20Oak%20Ridge%20National%20Laboratory%20in%20the%20US%2C%20acknowledged%20Microsoft's%20progress%20but%20pointed%20to%20the%20need%20for%20further%20development.%20%26quot%3BThe%20long-term%20goals%20for%20solving%20industrial%20applications%20on%20quantum%20computers%20will%20require%20scaling%20up%20these%20prototypes%20even%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20can%20quantum%20computing%20impact%20daily%20life%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuantum%20computers%20operate%20using%20qubits%2C%20which%20can%20process%20information%20in%20a%20fundamentally%20different%20way%20than%20classical%20computers.%20This%20shift%20could%20bring%20breakthroughs%20in%20multiple%20fields%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHealthcare%20and%20Medicine%3A%20Quantum%20computing%20can%20help%20design%20new%20drugs%20by%20simulating%20molecular%20interactions%2C%20leading%20to%20faster%20cures%20for%20diseases%20and%20better-personalised%20treatments.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEnvironment%20and%20Sustainability%3A%20It%20could%20create%20self-healing%20materials%20for%20infrastructure%2C%20reducing%20the%20need