0Tesla%20in%20the%20US%20is%20c.USD35k.%20With%20tariff%20lowered%20to%20c.15-%2020%20per%20cent%20in%20India%2C%20along%20with%20road%20tax%2C%20insurance%20and%20other%20costs%2C%20on-road%20price%20would%20be%20c.USD40k%2C%20which%20is%20close%20to%20Rs3.5-4m%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Tesla%20positions%20the%20Model%203%20at%20a%20price%2020-50%20per%20cent%20higher%20than%20domestic%20EV%20models%20like%20Mahindra%20XEV%209e%2C%20Hyundai%20e-Creta%2C%20and%20Maruti%20Suzuki%20e-Vitara%2C%20the%20report%20added%20that%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20disrupt%20the%20Indian%20EV%20market%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20Tesla%20decides%20to%20launch%20an%20entry-level%20model%20priced%20below%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20on-road%20and%20gains%20market%20share%2C%20the%20report%20believes%20that%20the%20recent%20decline%20in%20Mahindra%20%26amp%3B%20Mahindra's%20stock%20is%20already%20factoring%20in%20this%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20report%20suggests%20that%20Tesla's%20entry%20would%20not%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20major%20Indian%20automakers%2C%20as%20the%20overall%20penetration%20of%20EVs%20in%20India%20remains%20lower%20than%20in%20China%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvery-unfair-donald-trump-on-elon-musks-tesla-building-factory-in-india-7750962%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20would%20be%20launching%20its%20models%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftesla-begins-hiring-in-india-check-job-openings-and-locations-7738951%5C%22%3ETesla%20has%20officially%20begun%20its%20hiring%20process%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20its%20long-anticipated%20entry%20into%20the%20domestic%20market.%20On%20February%2018%2C%20the%20electric%20vehicle%20(EV)%20giant%20posted%20a%20job%20listing%20on%20LinkedIn%20for%20the%20position%20of%20Consumer%20Engagement%20Manager%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20Metropolitan%20Region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20outlined%20that%20Tesla%20would%20need%20to%20set%20up%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20India%20to%20make%20its%20cars%20more%20affordable%20and%20scale%20up%20its%20operations%2C%20even%20if%20import%20duties%20are%20reduced%20to%20below%2020%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20highlighted%20that%20under%20India's%20electric%20vehicle%20(EV)%20policy%2C%20Tesla%20could%20benefit%20from%20a%20lower%20import%20duty%20of%2015%20per%20cent%20on%20up%20to%208%2C000%20units%20per%20year%20if%20it%20invests%20over%20Rs%204150%20crore%20billion%20in%20setting%20up%20a%20local%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20draws%20a%20comparison%20with%20the%20Indian%20motorcycle%20market%2C%20where%20Harley-Davidson's%20X440%2C%20priced%2020%20per%20cent%20higher%20than%20the%20Royal%20Enfield%20Classic%20350%2C%20sells%20only%20around%201%2C500%20units%20per%20month%2C%20whereas%20the%20Classic%20350%20sells%20about%2028%2C000%20units%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20suggests%20that%20Indian%20consumers%20are%20highly%20price-sensitive%2C%20making%20it%20challenging%20for%20Tesla%20to%20gain%20traction%20without%20competitive%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-have-elon-musks-tesla-stores-soon-check-their-electric-cars-features-prices-7744567%5C%22%3ETesla's%20entry%20into%20the%20Indian%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20depends%20on%20whether%20it%20is%20willing%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20investment%20in%20local%20manufacturing.%20Without%20it%2C%20even%20with%20reduced%20import%20duties%2C%20Tesla's%20cars%20may%20remain%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20Indian%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%2