7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edestroy%20%3C%2Fa%3EIsrael%20as%20part%20of%20Operation%20True%20Promise%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20General%20Jbbari%20warned%20that%20%26quot%3BOperation%20True%20Promise%203%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%20with%20precision%2C%20and%20on%20a%20scale%20sufficient%20to%20destroy%20Israel%20and%20raze%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20Haifa%20to%20the%20ground.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Foreign%20Minister%20Gideon%20Sa'ar%20responded%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Jewish%20people%20have%20learned%20anything%20from%20history%2C%20it%20is%20this%3A%20if%20your%20enemy%20says%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20annihilate%20you%20-%20believe%20him.%20We%20are%20ready.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJabbari's%20comments%20mark%20the%20third%20such%20threat%20in%20a%20week%20from%20high-ranking%20IRGC%20officials.%20Brigadier%20General%20Ali%20Fadavi%2C%20deputy%20commander%20of%20the%20IRGC%2C%20and%20Brigadier%20General%20Amir%20Ali%20Hajizadeh%2C%20commander%20of%20the%20IRGC's%20Aerospace%20Force%2C%20have%20also%20issued%20similar%20statements%20vowing%20to%20destroy%20Israel%20as%20part%20of%20Operation%20True%20Promise%203%2C%20the%20planned%20third%20attack%20against%20Israel%20following%20Iranian%20strikes%20in%20April%20and%20October%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heightened%20rhetoric%20has%20reportedly%20coincided%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20IRGC%20missile%20production.%20Iran%20recently%20received%20a%201%2C000-ton%20shipment%20of%20rocket%20fuel%20precursor%20chemicals%20from%20China%2C%20claimed%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fmiddle-east%2Farticle-842197%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20IRGC%20unveiled%20a%20new%20underground%20%26quot%3Bmissile%20city%26quot%3B%2C%20%C2%A0an%20underground%20missile%20base%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20to%20target%20destroyers%20in%20strategic%20so