and%202021.%20Even%20rules%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20forest%20land%20were%20violated%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20found%20that%20funds%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%2014%20crore%20from%20the%20Compensatory%20Afforestation%20Fund%20Management%20and%20Planning%20Authority%20(CAMPA)%20-%20which%20works%20to%20mitigate%20the%20impact%20of%20forest%20land%20diversion%20-%20were%20diverted%20for%20other%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20funds%20were%20used%20to%20buy%20laptops%2C%20laptops%2C%20fridges%2C%20and%20coolers%2C%20besides%20other%20purposes%20like%20renovation%20of%20buildings%20and%20paying%20for%20court%20cases%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAMPA%20manages%20funds%20collected%20for%20forest%20land%20but%20diverted%20to%20non-forest%20uses.%20Their%20guidelines%20suggest%20afforestation%20should%20be%20carried%20out%20within%20a%20year%20or%20two%20growing%20seasons%20after%20getting%20the%20funds%2C%20but%20the%20report%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20took%20over%20eight%20years%20to%20conduct%20compensatory%20afforestation%20in%2037%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20has%20also%20flagged%20the%20selection%20of%20land%20in%20a%20wrongful%20manner%20under%20the%20CAMPA%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20forest%20land%20transfer%20rules%20were%20also%20ignored.%20It%20said%20the%20centre%20had%20given%20in-principle%20approval%20for%20non-forestry%20work%20like%20road%2C%20power%20lines%2C%20water%20supply%20lines%2C%20railways%2C%20and%20off-road%20lines%2C%20but%20permission%20from%20the%20Divisional%20Forest%20Officer%20(DFO)%20was%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2052%20cases%20between%202014%20and%202022%2C%20work%20was%20started%20without%20the%20DFO's%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20also%20flagged%20a%20low%20survival%20rate%20of%20the%20planted%20trees.%20During%202017-22%2C%20it%20was%20only%2033%25%2C%20lower%20than%20the%2060-65%25%20mandated%20by%20the%20Forest%20Research%20Institute%2C%20the%20report%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20flagged%20the%20distribution%20of%20expired%20medicines%20in%20government%20hospitals.%20At%20least%20three%20government%20hospitals%20had%20stocks%20of%2034%20expired%20medicines%20and%20some%20of%20those%20had%20expired%20over%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20also%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20new%20rules%20in%20view%20of%20a%20shortage%20of%20super%20specialist%20doctors%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20At%20least%2070%25%20of%20posts%20for%20specialist%20doctors%20in%20the%20hilly%20areas%20and%2050%25%20of%20such%20posts%20in%20the%20plains%20are%20vacant%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20250%20doctors%20were%20allowed%20to%20continue%20despite%20violating%20the%20lockdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20has%20used%20the%20findings%20to%20accuse%20the%20government%20of%20wasting%20public%20funds%2C%20Uttarakhand%20Forest%20Minister%20Subodh%20Uniyal%20has%20said%20he%20has%20ordered%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20matter%20related%20to%20his%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740198720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fnr0h647g_uttarakhand-forest_625x300_22_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-cag-report-central-audit-finds-forest-funds-used-for-buying-iphones-laptops-in-uttarakhand-7767237%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20central%20audit%20has%20found%20massive%20financial%20irregularities%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20including%20the%20use%20of%20funds%20meant%20for%20forest%20conservation%20for%20buying%20iPhones%20and%20office%20decor%20items%2C%20besides%20the%20violation%20of%20other%20rules.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Leaders'%20Sleepover%20At%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20After%20%26q