grandmother)%20Indira%20Gandhi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20Tika%20Ram%20Jully%20strongly%20objected%20to%20the%20minister's%20remarks%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Binappropriate%20word%26quot%3B%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20record.%20Several%20Congress%20MLAs%20then%20started%20sloganeering%20and%20moved%20towards%20the%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Jogaram%20Patel%2C%20however%2C%20said%20there%20was%20nothing%20unparliamentary%20about%20the%20word%20'dadi'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUproar%20In%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20was%20initially%20adjourned%20for%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20then%20till%202%20pm%20and%20again%20till%204%20pm.%20When%20proceedings%20resumed%20at%204%20pm%2C%20%C2%A0government%20chief%20whip%20Jogeshwar%20Garg%20said%20the%20opposition%20had%20crossed%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20speed%20and%20intention%20with%20which%20they%20moved%20towards%20the%20chair%20and%20the%20incident%20of%20reaching%20close%20to%20the%20Speaker%20is%20definitely%20condemnable%20and%20not%20a%20pardonable%20crime.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20request%20that%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20indecent%20and%20condemnable%20conduct%20of%20the%20opposition%20members%20in%20the%20House%2C%20the%20following%20members%20should%20be%20suspended%20for%20the%20remaining%20period%20of%20the%20current%20budget%20session...%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasara%2C%20Ramkesh%20Meena%2C%20Amin%20Kagzi%2C%20Jakir%20Hussain%2C%20Hakim%20Ali%20and%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jully%20later%20said%20the%20minister%20had%20made%20%26quot%3Bindecent%26quot%3B%20comments%20and%20the%20BJP's%20attitude%20was%20one%20of%20suppressing%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMinister%20Shri%20Avinash%20Gehlot%20made%20indecent%20comments%20about%20respected%20leader%20Indira%20Gandhi%20ji%2C%20who%20sacrificed%20her%20life%20for%20the%20country%2C%20but%20our%20MLAs%20were%20suspended.%20This%20shows%20that%20the%20BJP%20only%20wants%20to%20work%20with%20a%20dictatorial%20attitude.%20Not%20allowing%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20to%20deliver%20his%20speech%20on%20the%20Governor's%20address%20and%20now%20suspending%206%20MLAs%2C%20including%20the%20state%20(Congress)%20president%2C%20is%20the%20result%20of%20the%20BJP's%20thinking%20of%20suppressing%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%20in%20Hindi.%3Cbr%3E%5CnSenior%20party%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma-led%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20was%20trying%20to%20hide%20its%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20a%20minister%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20made%20an%20indecent%20comment%20on%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20then%20suspended%20the%20Congress%20MLAs%20from%20the%20House%20who%20protested%20against%20not%20apologising%20for%20it.%20This%20shows%20that%20the%20method%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20being%20adopted%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20as%20well.%20Just%20like%20MPs%20are%20suspended%20there%20to%20hide%20their%20failures%2C%20the%20same%20has%20been%20done%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20had%20no%20work%20to%20show%20in%20the%20last%20one%20year%2C%20so%20the%20Leader%20of%20opposition%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20give%20a%20speech%20highlighting%20its%20failures%20during%20the%20address.%20Now%20our%20state%20president%20and%20MLAs%20from%20Dalit%2C%20backward%2C%20tribal%20and%20minority%20communities%20have%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20Budget%20session.%20Is%20this%20not%20an%20attempt%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20Budget%2C%26quo