%20of%20the%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%20Air%20Force%20Gen.%20Charles%20Q.%20Brown%20Jr.%2C%20which%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20string%20of%20firings%20in%20the%20Pentagon's%20most%20senior%20ranks%20that%20alarmed%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%20posted%20Friday%20night%2C%20Secretary%20of%20Defense%20Pete%20Hegseth%20also%20removed%20the%20chief%20of%20naval%20operations%20and%20the%20Air%20Force%20vice%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20Adm.%20Lisa%20Franchetti%20and%20Gen.%20James%20Slife%2C%20respectively%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20top%20military%20lawyers%20for%20the%20Army%2C%20Navy%2C%20and%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20removals%20of%20confirmed%20leaders%20deepen%20the%20turmoil%20at%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20which%20faces%20deep%20cuts%20to%20its%20civilian%20workforce%20and%20budget%20shifts%20that%20Trump%20officials%20say%20are%20to%20align%20with%20the%20new%20administration's%20priorities.%20Nearly%205%2C400%20probationary%20employees%20within%20the%20DoD%20may%20face%20job%20termination%20next%20week%2C%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20slew%20of%20cuts%20that%20could%20total%20around%2055%2C000%20civilian%20military%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2222b71728-942d-44f1-b81a-941bb1e56824%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFriday%20night%20firings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20Truth%20Social%20announcement%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20did%20not%20provide%20a%20reason%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20the%20president's%20top%20military%20advisor%2C%20nor%20did%20he%20explain%20the%20move%20to%20replace%20Brown%20with%20a%20retired%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20is%20a%20fighter%20pilot%2C%20and%20only%20the%20second%20African%20American%20to%20hold%20the%20chairman%20position.%20After%20the%20police%20killing%20of%20George%20Floyd%20in%202020%2C%20Brown%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-chief-racial-injus