0Avera%20Mengistu%2C%2039%2C%20have%20been%20held%20by%20Hamas%20since%20they%20entered%20Gaza%20separately%20under%20unexplained%20circumstances%20around%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20return%2C%20Israel%20is%20expected%20to%20release%20602%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20and%20detainees%20held%20in%20its%20jails%20in%20the%20latest%20stage%20of%20an%20exchange%20that%20has%20held%20up%20despite%20a%20series%20of%20problems%20that%20have%20come%20close%20to%20sinking%20it%20on%20different%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Israel%20accused%20Hamas%20of%20violating%20the%20ceasefire%20by%20handing%20over%20an%20unidentified%20body%20instead%20of%20the%20remains%20of%20hostage%20Shiri%20Bibas%20that%20were%20due%20to%20be%20returned%20along%20with%20the%20bodies%20of%20her%20two%20small%20sons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20her%20remains%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20mixed%20up%20with%20other%20human%20remains%20recovered%20from%20the%20rubble%20after%20an%20Israeli%20air%20strike%20that%20it%20said%20killed%20her%20and%20her%20two%20sons%20in%20November%202023.%20On%20Friday%2C%20the%20group%20handed%20over%20another%20body%2C%20which%20Israeli%20forensic%20officials%20were%20preparing%20to%20investigate%20to%20confirm%20the%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bibas%20family%2C%20kidnapped%20along%20with%20their%20father%20in%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20has%20been%20an%20emblem%20of%20the%20trauma%20suffered%20by%20Israel%20on%20that%20day%20and%20the%20misidentification%20of%20the%20remains%20of%20Shiri%20Bibas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20staged%20handover%20of%20their%20coffins%20by%20Hamas%20outraged%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20intelligence%20assessments%20and%20forensic%20analysis%20of%20the%20bodies%20of%2010-month-old%20Kfir%20Bibas%20and%20his%20four-year-old%20brother%20Ariel%20showed%20both%20had%20been%20killed%20deliberately%20by%20their%20captors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20threatened%20to%20make%20Hamas%20%26quot%3Bpay%20the%20full%20price%26quot%3B%20for%20failing%20to%20return%20the%20body%20but%20he%20held%20back%20from%20walking%20away%20from%20the%20ceasefire%20agreement%2C%20which%20took%20effect%20on%20Jan.%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20which%20has%20itself%20accused%20Israel%20of%20breaching%20the%20ceasefire%20by%20blocking%20vital%20aid%20supplies%20into%20Gaza%2C%20nonetheless%20formally%20informed%20Israel%20of%20the%20names%20of%20the%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20on%20Saturday%20in%20a%20sign%20the%20handover%20would%20go%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceasefire%20has%20brought%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20fighting%20but%20prospects%20of%20a%20definitive%20end%20to%20the%20war%20remain%20unclear.%20Hamas%2C%20which%20killed%20some%201%2C200%20people%20and%20took%20251%20hostages%20during%20its%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20has%20been%20at%20pains%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20it%20remains%20in%20control%20in%20Gaza%20despite%20heavy%20losses%20in%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20campaign%20killed%20at%20least%2048%2C000%20people%2C%20according%20to%20Palestinian%20health%20authorities%2C%20and%20reduced%20much%20of%20the%20enclave%20to%20rubble%2C%20leaving%20some%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20in%20makeshift%20shelters%20and%20dependent%20on%20aid%20trucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20have%20said%20they%20intend%20to%20start%20talks%20on%20a%20second%20stage%2C%20which%20mediators%20say%20aim%20to%20agree%20the%20return%20of%20around%2060%20remaining%20hostages%20and%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Israeli%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20hopes%20of%20a%20deal%20have%20been%20clouded%20by%20disagreements%20over%20the%20future%20of%20Gaza%2C%20that%20have%20been%20deepened%20by%20shock%20across%20the%20region%20over%20U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20proposal%20to%20clear%20the%20enclave%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20develop%20it%20as%20a%20Riv