mpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zelensky%20can%20change%20Trump's%20mind%20on%20support%2C%20says%20Ukraine%20official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740183873000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fea59%2Flive%2F433bcee0-f0b3-11ef-9e61-71ee71f26eb1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcz9nxx82xvqo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ihor%20Brusylo%20told%20the%20BBC's%20Jeremy%20Bowen%20that%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20stance%20on%20the%20war%20was%20%26quot%3Balarming%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcz9nxx82xvqo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kash%20Patel%20Sworn%20In%20As%20FBI%20Director%2C%20Takes%20Oath%20On%20Bhagavad%20Gita%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian-American%20Kash%20Patel%20was%20officially%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%20ninth%20Director%20of%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(FBI)%20on%20Friday%2C%20taking%20the%20oath%20on%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel's%20girlfriend%20and%20family%20stood%20beside%20him%20as%20he%20recited%20the%20oath%2C%20and%20other%20family%20members%20were%20seated%20in%20the%20front%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKash%20Patel%20was%20sworn%20in%20at%20the%20Eisenhower%20Executive%20Office%20Building%20by%20US%20Attorney%20General%20Pam%20Bondi%20after%20being%20confirmed%20by%20the%20US%20Senate%20as%20the%20ninth%20FBI%20director%2C%20succeeding%20Christopher%20Wray%2C%20Fox%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20oath%2C%20Patel%20said%20that%20he%20was%20living%20the%20American%20dream%20and%20added%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bfirst-generation%20Indian%20is%20about%20to%20lead%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agency%20of%20the%20greatest%20nation%20on%20earth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20