.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Navy%20spends%20roughly%20%2440%20billion%20annually%20on%20shipbuilding%20projects%2C%20yet%20these%20projects%20are%20regularly%20behind%20schedule%20and%20battling%20rising%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20Department%20of%20the%20Navy%20review%20found%20that%20top%20programs%2C%20such%20as%20Block%20IV%20Virginia-class%20attack%20submarines%2C%20the%20Pentagon's%20priority%20Columbia-class%20ballistic%20missile%20submarine%2C%20the%20Constellation-class%20guided-missile%20frigate%2C%20and%20the%20next%20Ford-class%20carrier%2C%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-us-navy-shipbuilding-projects-are-delayed-by-years-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall%20severely%20delayed%20and%20over%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20COVID's%20impact%20on%20the%20workforce%20and%20supply%20chain%2C%20%26quot%3Bwith%20industry%20reticent%20to%20invest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%20said%20previously%20it%20had%20observed%20consistent%20issues%2C%20too%2C%20with%20the%20Navy's%20cost%20estimates%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bare%20often%20lacking%20and%20the%20assumptions%20unrealistic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20did%20not%20have%20new%20comments%20to%20share%20on%20shipbuilding%20problems%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publishing%2C%20pointing%20Business%20Insider%20instead%20to%20past%20remarks%20by%20service%20leaders.%20Previously%2C%20the%20Navy%20has%20often%20put%20the%20burden%20on%20industry%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20complex%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20budget%20shifts%20within%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20amid%20changing%20priorities%20for%20a%20new%20administration%20may%20further%20impact%20the%20industry%2C%20though%20the%20plans%20remain%20unclear%20for%20the%20time%20being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hudson.org%2Fevents%2Frighting-ship-strengthening-us-navy-shipbuilding-ship-repair-bryan-