7%23jonathan-graham-aquatic-capital-management-17%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAquatic%20Capital%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20buzziest%20quant%20fund%20launches%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20said%20four%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20to%20discuss%20private%20information.%20Paloma%20seeded%20Aquatic%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20by%20the%20Citadel%20alum%20Jonathan%20Graham%20in%202019.%20It%20has%20%24360%20million%20invested%20with%20Aquatic%2C%20which%20is%20subject%20to%20lock-up%20terms%20and%20can%20be%20redeemed%20in%20tranches%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaloma%20has%20also%20put%20into%20the%20special-purpose%20vehicle%20%E2%80%94%20called%20Dove%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20portfolio%20of%20commercial-mortgage-backed%20securities%20valued%20at%20%24240%20million%2C%20which%20are%20set%20to%20be%20sold%20off%20over%20time%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%20The%20portfolio%20was%20previously%20managed%20as%20a%20separate%20account%20by%20Cannae%20Portfolio%20Advisors%2C%20a%20credit%20fund%20that%20has%20managed%20Paloma%20money%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Paloma%20representative%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaloma%20is%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20and%20most%20venerated%20hedge%20funds.%20Founded%20by%20Donald%20Sussman%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20it%20is%20best%20known%20for%20seeding%20the%20quant%20giant%20D.%20E.%20Shaw%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20bets%20on%20LMR%20Partners%2C%20Squarepoint%20Capital%2C%20and%20Sona%20Asset%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Paloma%20is%20off%20to%20a%20strong%20start%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20up%202.5%25%20through%20mid-February%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20performance%20said%20%E2%80%94%20the%20firm%20has%20struggled%20with%20performance%20in%20recent%20years%20and%20has%20overhauled%20its%20C-suite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fund%20brought%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsides-neil-chrisss-short-stint-atop-paloma-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehedge%20fund%20veteran%20Neil%20Chriss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20formerly%20of%20Millennium%20and%20Hutchin%20Hill%20Capital%2C%20in%202023%20to%20lead%20the%20firm.%20But%20he%20lasted%20less%20than%20a%20year.%20He%20was%20replaced%20by%20Ravi%20Singh%2C%20an%20alum%20of%20Credit%20Suisse's%20asset%20management%20division%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20where%20he%20held%20leadership%20positions%20in%20prime%20brokerage%2C%20equity%20derivatives%2C%20and%20equities%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaloma%20gained%20just%202.5%25%20in%202024%2C%20which%20was%20generally%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2024-hedge-funds-returns-performance-schonfeld-citadel-millennium-deshaw-walleye-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebumper%20year%20for%20hedge%20fund%20managers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it%20has%20averaged%203.6%25%20over%20the%20past%20three%20full%20years%2C%20according%20to%20performance%20figures%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20A%20composite%20hedge%20fund%20index%20returned%206.6%25%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20the%20industry%20research%20firm%20PivotalPath%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaloma's%20assets%20under%20management%20have%20fallen%20to%20%241.7%20billion%2C%20down%20from%20about%20%244%20billion%20when%20Chriss%20took%20the%20helm%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ca57b5d-4c6d-40c7-a21f-2b32028fa393%5C%22%3EAssets%20in%20Dove%20to%20be%20sold%20over%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20redemption%20requests%20piling%20up%2C%20Paloma%20told%20its%20limited%20partners%20in%20November%20it%20would%20be%20able%20to%20pay%20them%20only%2030%25%20in%20up-front%20cash%20and%20the%20rest%20over%20time%20as%20it%20liquidated%20holdings%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported.%20%3Cspan%3EUltimately%2C%20Paloma%20paid%20half%20the%20%241.2%20billion%20balance%20in%20cash%2C%20with%20the%20remaining%20%24600%20million%20to%20be%20distributed%20as%20it%20winds%20down%20assets%20in%20Dove%2C%20the%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%20Paloma%20will%20not%20charge%20fees%20on%20the%20vehicle%2C%20which%20is%20being%20administered%20by%20PwC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESystematic%20trading%20outfits%2C%20reliant%20on%20technology%20and%20data%2C%20typically%20require%20years%20of%20patience%20to%20yield%20results%2C%20but%20Aquatic%20has%20nonetheless%20gotten%20off%20to%20a%20slow%20start.%20It%20launched%20in%202019%20with%20%24500%20million%20in%20commitments%20from%20Paloma%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported%2C%20and%20its%20assets%20later%20hit%20%241.5%20billion%20with%20capital%20from%20investors%20including%20the%20Teacher%20Retirement%20System%20of%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAquatic%20lost%203.3%25%20between%20September%202023%20and%20September%202024%2C%20according%20to%20returns%20from%20the%20Teacher%20Retirement%20System%20of%20Texas%2C%20a%20public%20pension.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frenaissance-technologies-marshall-wace-quant-hedge-fund-performance-returns-2024-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuant%20hedge%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20among%20the%20industry's%20best%20performers%20in%202024%2C%20gaining%2014.2%25%20on%20average%2C%20according%20to%20PivotalPath's%20equity%20quant%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAquatic%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECannae%2C%20which%20specializes%20in%20structured%20products%2C%20was%20spun%20out%20of%20Paloma%20in%202020%20and%20raised%20external%20capital.%20It%20continued%20to%20manage%20a%20structured-credit%20portfolio%20for%20Paloma%20through%20a%20separate%20account%2C%20composed%20primarily%20of%20commercial-mortgage-backed%20securities.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-debt-property-losses-mortgage-interest-rates-prices-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECommercial%20real%20estate%20has%20taken%20a%20beating%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20with%20many%20bonds%20trading%20below%20par%2C%20liquidating%20holdings%20would%20in%20many%20cases%20mean%20locking%20in%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20assets%20have%20fallen%20and%20Paloma%20has%20had%20to%20pull%20capital%20from%20external%20managers%2C%20the%20fund%20isn't%20finished%20allocating.%20Geoffrey%20Lauprete%2C%20the%20ex-chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20WorldQuant%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20launch%20his%20own%20fund%20later%20this%20year%20with%20backing%20from%20Paloma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaloma%20has%20also%20revamped%20its%20C-suite.%20Apart%20from%20Singh%2C%20it%20has%20recently%20hired%20new%20executives%20to%20manage%20finance%2C%20risk%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20marketing.%20Michael%20DeAddio%2C%20the%20president%20and%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20WorldQuant%20until%202020%2C%20joined%20in%20December%2C%20and%20Louis%20Molinari%2C%20the%20global%20head%20of%20capital%20introduction%20and%20hedge%20fund%20consulting%20at%20Barclays%20until%202024%2C%20joined%20as%20the%20firm's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECorrection%3A%20February%2021%2C%202025%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20An%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20story%20misstated%20that%20Blackstone%20was%20an%20investor%20in%20Aquatic.%20Blackstone%20is%20not%20an%20Aquatic%20investor.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaloma-partners-investor-redemption-plan-pulls-aquatic-cannae-capital-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740168113000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b8c6834e7cbbbe3dc43604%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaloma-partners-investor-redem