0Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20has%20built%20a%20close%20relationship%20with%20Anthropic%20in%20recent%20years.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20funding%2C%20Anthropic%20agreed%20to%20use%20Amazon's%20cloud%20computing%20services%20and%20AI%20chips.%20Last%20year%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20use%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-new-planned-supercomputer-at-aws-conference-trainium-nova-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20supercomputer%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20up%20of%20Amazon-made%20chip%20clusters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20total%20investment%20value%20in%20public%20and%20private%20companies%20was%20%2422.1%20billion%20as%20of%20the%20end%20of%20December%2C%20the%20filing%20said.%20Publicly%20traded%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20Rivian%2C%20accounted%20for%20just%20%244.6%20billion.%20Among%20the%20private%20companies%20Amazon%20invested%20in%20are%20Scale%20AI%2C%20Hugging%20Face%2C%20and%20X-energy%2C%20according%20to%20Pitchbook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20at%20Amazon%3F%20Got%20a%20tip%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EContact%20the%20reporter%20Eugene%20Kim%20via%20the%20encrypted%20messaging%20apps%20Signal%20or%20Telegram%20(%2B1-650-942-3061)%20or%20email%20(%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aekim%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eekim%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E).%20Reach%20out%20using%20a%20nonwork%20device.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ECheck%20out%20Insider's%20source%20guide%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20f