3EPride%20Fund%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20pioneering%20role%20in%20India%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3EPride%20Fund%3C%2Fem%3E%20marks%20a%20historic%20milestone%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20initiative%20in%20India%2C%20created%20by%20queer%20community%20members%20for%20the%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20fund%20reflects%20our%20shared%20vision%20of%20equity%20and%20inclusion%20by%20directly%20tackling%20the%20systemic%20barriers%20that%20have%20long%20marginalised%20LGBTQIA%2B%20individuals.%20With%20only%2027%25%20of%20NGOs%20serving%20the%20community%20having%20a%20national%20presence%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20empower%20these%20communities%20by%20providing%20targeted%20support%20and%20resources.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20access%20to%20safety%2C%20health%2C%20justice%2C%20and%20opportunities%20that%20have%20been%20denied%20to%20them%20for%20far%20too%20long.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20addressing%20these%20pressing%20needs%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20create%20a%20ripple%20effect%20that%20leads%20to%20a%20more%20inclusive%20and%20equitable%20society%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20truly%20embodies%20the%20spirit%20of%20a%20Viksit%20Bharat%2C%20where%20every%20individual%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20identity%2C%20can%20thrive%20with%20dignity%20and%20pride.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhika%20Piramal%2C%20who%20identifies%20as%20a%20lesbian%20and%20married%20her%20wife%2C%20Amanda%2C%20in%20London%2C%20reflected%20on%20the%20painful%20impact%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20October%202023%20ruling%20against%20marriage%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20else%20do%20we%20go%20but%20back%20to%20the%20people%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20at%20the%20launch%20event%2C%20held%20at%20the%20Godrej%20One%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20legally%20register%20my%20marriage%20with%20my%20wife%20in%20India.%20That%20reality%20is%20deeply%20unfair%2