ress-file-70-1739871807-300x186.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-70-1739871807-500x310.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-70-1739871807-150x93.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-406821%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22385%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EElephants%20migrated%20to%20the%20Udanti-Sitanadi%20Tiger%20Reserve%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20food%20and%20shelter.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EM%3C%2Fem%3Eunaadi%20alert%20system%20was%20used%2C%20in%20which%20a%20%3Cem%3EKotwar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20village%20messenger)%20beat%20drums%20and%20used%20a%20microphone%20to%20warn%20villagers%20of%20approaching%20elephants.%20However%2C%20in%20April%202022%2C%20a%20tragic%20incident%20highlighted%20the%20limitations%20of%20this%20method.%20An%20elephant%20unexpectedly%20changed%20direction%2C%20entering%20a%20village%20that%20had%20not%20been%20warned%20in%20time%2C%20leading%20to%20three%20human%20casualties%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20my%20first%20time%20witnessing%20a%20human%20fatality%2C%20and%20I%20was%20there%20for%20the%20post-mortem%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20me.%20I%20realised%20we%20needed%20a%20faster%2C%20more%20reliable%20alert%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20AI%20into%20the%20picture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20find%20a%20technological%20solution%2C%20Varun%20and%20his%20team%20developed%20a%20basic%20application%20in%20February%202023.%20The%20system%20collected%20elephant%20movement%20data%20from%20foot%20patrolling%20teams%20and%20shared%20it%20with%20villagers%20via%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Varun%20soon%20connected%20with%20Kalpvaig%20Technologies%2C%20a%20Ghaziabad-based%20startup%2C%20which%20suggested%20automating%20the%20process%20using%20AI.%20The%20collaboration%20resulted%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Chhattisgarh%20Elephant%20Tracking%20and%20Alert%20System%E2%80%99%2C%20formally%20launched%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20it%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFoot%20officers%20use%20an%20ODK%20(Open%20Data%20Kit)%20app%2C%20a%20free%20Google%20tool%2C%20to%20identify%20elephants%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360895%2Fvivek-menon-wildlife-trust-of-india-wildlife-conservation-anti-poaching-elephant-corridors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrack%20their%20movements%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20herd%20details%2C%20faecal%20matter%2C%20pug%20marks%2C%20and%20damages%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Om%20Prakash%20Rao%2C%20a%20beat%20forest%20officer.%20Since%20connectivity%20in%20the%20jungle%20is%20poor%2C%20the%20data%20is%20stored%20offline%20and%20syncs%20once%20network%20access%20is%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFoot%20patrol%20officers%20are%20crucial%20in%20this%20process.%20These%20officers%2C%20often%20working%20in%20risky%20conditions%2C%20navigate%20dense%20forests%20and%20confront%20potential%20elephant%20encounters%20to%20gather%20real-time%20data.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20times%20when%20we%20have%20escaped%20a%20massive%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Om%20Prakash.%20Their%20efforts%20ensure%20accurate%20tracking%2C%20forming%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20AI%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-71_11zon-1739872094.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Foot%20officers%20documenting%20elephant%20movements%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-71_11zon-1739872094.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-71_11zon-1739872094-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-71_11zon-1739872094-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-71_11zon-1739872094-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-406833%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22349%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20foot%20officers%20add%20the%20information%20to%20the%20service%20via%20the%20app.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recorded%20data%20is%20processed%20using%20Quantum%20GIS%20(QGIS)%2C%20an%20open-source%20mapping%20software%20which%20plots%20elephant%20movements%20and%20sets%20a%2010-km%20buffer%20zone%20around%20the%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20automatically%20sends%20alerts%20via%20SMSs%2C%20calls%2C%20and%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20to%20registered%20villagers%2C%20local%20leaders%2C%20and%20forest%20department%20officials%20in%20at-risk%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20install%20any%20app%3B%20they%20just%20need%20to%20register%20their%20mobile%20numbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%