%9CThese%20collars%20are%20usually%20put%20on%20the%20female%20elephant%20of%20the%20herd%2C%20which%20is%20the%20leader.%20But%20elephants%20are%20very%20intelligent%3B%20they%20manage%20to%20remove%20the%20collars%20in%20about%20two%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Varun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20manual%20screening%20by%20foot%20patrolling%20officers%20remains%20the%20most%20viable%20option%2C%20with%20the%20Government%20placing%20greater%20emphasis%20on%20improving%20ground%20surveillance.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20absence%20of%20GPS%20collars%2C%20we%20rely%20heavily%20on%20our%20forest%20teams%E2%80%99%20vigilance%20and%20data%20collection%20to%20make%20real-time%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Varun.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20role%20is%20irreplaceable%20in%20this%20ecosystem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20lives%20and%20understanding%20elephant%20behaviour%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20AI-powered%20system%20in%20February%202023%2C%20no%20human%20fatalities%20have%20been%20reported%20for%2022%20months%20%E2%80%94%20a%20significant%20drop%20from%20the%20previous%20annual%20average%20of%20five%20to%20six%20deaths.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20have%20one%20casualty%20in%20December%202024%2C%20but%20the%20family%20was%20intoxicated%20and%20unable%20to%20escape%20despite%20receiving%20an%20hour%E2%80%99s%20warning%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20saving%20lives%2C%20the%20system%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343739%2Fhuman-animal-tiger-conflict-in-chandrapur-maharashtra-reduced-with-ai-tech-wildlife-eye-innovation-valiance%2