le%20QR%20plates%2C%20and%20are%20being%20monitored%20and%20safeguarded%20using%20cutting%20edge%20tech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20ultrasonography-based%20(USG)%20gadgets%2C%20we%20can%20assess%20the%20health%20and%20risk%20levels%20of%20each%20chinar%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20manual%20evaluation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tariq%20explains.%20This%20technology%20allows%20for%20early%20detection%20of%20vulnerabilities%20and%20targeted%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20Forest%20Department%2C%20spearheading%20the%20campaign%2C%20is%20utilising%20a%20Geographical%20Information%20System%20(GIS)%20to%20create%20a%20comprehensive%20database.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20will%20be%20crucial%20in%20protecting%20chinar%20trees%20from%20the%20threats%20of%20urbanisation%20and%20deforestation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tariq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201948px)%20100vw%2C%201948px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221948%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Each%20QR%20code%20provide%20information%20on%2025%20parameters%20about%20each%20China%20tree%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575.jpg%201948w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575-768x512.jpg